measurementGroup.name: AdmissionControl
measurementGroup.desc: Measurement group for Mo Class ns :ERBS_NODE_MODEL, name :AdmissionControl

measurementGroup.name: BbProcessingResource
measurementGroup.desc: Measurement group for Mo Class ns :ERBS_NODE_MODEL, name :BbProcessingResource

measurement.ns2:desc:
Distribution over ratio of number of RRC connected users with unknown ARP value over total number of RRC connected users in the eNodeB in UE Context admission control.
PDF ranges: [0] 0 %, [1] ]0..10] %, [2] ]10..20] %, [3] ]20..30]%, [4] ]30..40] %, [5] ]40..50] %, [6] ]50..60] %, [7] ]60..70] %, [8] ]70..80] %, [9] ]80..90] %, [10] ]90..100] %.

The X percentile of the utilization for downlink baseband capacity during a measurement period. The value for X is given by the attribute ENodeBFunction::licDlBbPercentileConf. The data that is evaluated is the same as for the counter BbProcessingResource::pmLicDlCapDistr. Source Data: ENodeBFunction::licDlBbPercentileConf and pmLicDlCapDistr
measurement.condition: Is calculated at the end of a ROP period.

measurement.ns2:desc:
Shows the utilization of DL baseband capacity relative to the minimum of installed license for DL Baseband Capacity or hardware capacity limit. Expressed as percentage of the minimum of license limit or hardware capacity limit.
PDF ranges: [0]: [0..5]%, [1]: ]5..10]%, [2]: ]10..15]%, [3]: ]15..20]%, [4]: ]20..25]%, [5]: ]25..30]%, [6]: ]30..35]%, [7]: ]35..40]%, [8]: ]40..45]%, [9]: ]45..50]%, [10]: ]50..55]%, [11]: ]55..60]%, [12]: ]60..65]%, [13]: ]65..70]%, [14]: ]70..75]%, [15]: ]75..80]%, [16]: ]80..85]%, [17]: ]85..90]%, [18]: ]90..95]%, [19]: ]95..100]%
Note: 0 on all bins is a reserved value set that indicates the cell has been disabled for the entire ROP. If cell is active, no utilization has occurred for the entire ROP.

The X percentile of the utilization for uplink baseband capacity during a measurement period. The value for X is given by the attribute ENodeBFunction::licUlBbPercentileConf. The data that is evaluated is the same as for the counter BbProcessingResource::pmLicUlCapDistr. Source Data: ENodeBFunction::licUlBbPercentileConf and pmLicUlCapDistr
measurement.condition: Is calculated at the end of a ROP period.

Counts the number of times the corresponding Sum counters has been incremented. Associated ACC pmCounter pmRohcCidSum.
measurement.condition: The counter is increased at every occasion when the corresponding sum counter is increased.

measurement.ns2:desc: Sum of all sample values recorded for the number of Robust Header Compression context Ids.
measurement.condition: At each time sampled measurement, the result is added to the existing aggregated value.

measurement.ns2:desc: Total number of downlink packets (unicast DRB PDCP SDUs or MBMS SYNC SDUs) discarded in the Ethernet part of the eNB.
measurement.condition: Discarded PDCP SDUs in the Ethernet part between GTP-u and PDCP layer.

measurement.ns2:desc: Number of DRB packets (PDCP SDUs) discarded in downlink due to that the specific Tunnel Endpoint Identifier (TEID) is not mapped to any UE context.
measurement.condition: Stepped when a downlink DRB packet (PDCP SDU) is discarded due to that the specific Tunnel Endpoint Identifier (TEID) is not mapped to any UE context.

measurement.ns2:desc: Normally this counter is not used, it can however sometimes be temporarily used for very late additions in a release. If so, for description see Network Impact Report in the CPI.

Number of downlink DRB packets (PDCP SDUs) discarded in the Ethernet part of the RBS due to that DL consistency check fails.
measurement.condition: Discarded PDCP SDUs in the Ethernet part between GTP-u and PDCP layer due to that DL consistency check fails.

measurement.ns2:desc: Number of downlink DRB packets (PDCP SDUs) discarded in the Ethernet part of the RBS due to DL Burst overload control.
measurement.condition: Discarded PDCP SDUs in the Ethernet part between GTP-u and PDCP layer due to DL Burst overload control

measurement.ns2:desc: Number of downlink DRB packets (PDCP SDUs) discarded in the Ethernet part of the RBS due to DL X2 Forwarding pacing functionality.
measurement.condition: Discarded PDCP SDUs in the Ethernet part between GTP-u and PDCP layer due to DL X2 Forwarding pacing functionality.

measurement.ns2:desc: Number of uplink DRB packets (PDCP SDUs) discarded in the Ethernet part of the RBS due UL pacing functionality.
measurement.condition: Discarded PDCP SDUs in the Ethernet part between GTP-u and PDCP layer due UL pacing functionality.

measurement.ns2:desc: Number of MBMS SYNC packets discarded in downlink due to an unidentified MBMS bearer.
measurement.condition: Stepped when a downlink MBMS SYNC packet is discarded due to an unidentified MBMS bearer.

measurement.ns2:desc: The number of times a PUCCH allocation request for SR resource(s) could not be granted due to lack of resources.
measurement.condition: SR resource request in a cell is not granted due to lack of BbProcessingResource SR processing capacity.

measurement.ns2:desc: The number of times a PUCCH allocation request for CQI resource(s) could not be granted due to lack of resources.
measurement.condition: CQI resource request in a cell is not granted due to lack of BbProcessingResource CQI processing capacity.

measurement.ns2:desc: Maximum utilization of SR resources in the BbProcessingResource.
measurement.condition: When resource utilization increased after a successful SR resource allocation.

measurement.ns2:desc: Maximum utilization of CQI resources in the BbProcessingResource.
measurement.condition: When resource utilization increased after a successful CQI resource allocation.
The counter is stepped periodically at each measurement interval of UL PRB utilization level for each baseband module.

The counter is stepped periodically at each measurement interval of DL baseband capacity utilization level for each baseband module.
